      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">52.244-5</ph> Competition in Subcontracting.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p " id="d3639e8">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="44.204.dita#FAR_44_204"
                     base="i1073622"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">44.204</xref>(c)</ph>, insert the following clause:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" id="d3639e15">
            Competition in Subcontracting (Aug 2024)
         </p>
         <ol id="d3596e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3639e21">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            The Contractor shall select subcontractors (including suppliers) on a competitive basis to the maximum practical extent consistent with the objectives and requirements of the contract.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3639e26">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  If the Contractor is an approved mentor under the DoD Mentor-Protégé Program (<xref href="https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title10-section4902&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">10 U.S.C. 4902</xref>), the Contractor may award subcontracts under this contract on a noncompetitive basis to its protégés.
               </p>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Endofclause">(End of clause)</p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
